---

<!-- Section 1: Executive Summary -->
<section data-section="executive-summary" class="proposal-section hidden">
  <div class="proposal-content">
    <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1B2A4A] mb-6">1. Executive Summary</h2>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      Cloud9 needs a tool that turns SharePoint data into interactive architecture visualisations.
      Consultants and their clients should be able to explore application landscapes, filter by any
      dimension, trace integration dependencies, and export what they see into slide decks and
      client-ready documents, without maintaining manual diagrams that go stale the moment they&rsquo;re drawn.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      The tool also represents a commercial opportunity. Each client deployment costs approximately $64
      per month in Azure infrastructure. Cloud9 determines the pricing model, with the margin per client
      being the difference between the chosen price point and the infrastructure cost.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      <strong>We propose building this tool in 8 weeks</strong> with a two-person senior development
      team, starting with a focused one-week discovery, four weeks of development, one week of UAT, and
      two weeks of hypercare support.
    </p>

    <!-- Key Numbers -->
    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1B2A4A] mt-8 mb-6">Key Numbers</h3>

    <!-- Investment -->
    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1B2A4A] mb-3">Investment</h4>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-4 text-center">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto mb-2 text-[#FF6B6B]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
        </svg>
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1B2A4A]">$42,700</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">MVP Investment (AUD)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-4 text-center">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto mb-2 text-[#FF6B6B]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
        </svg>
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1B2A4A]">30.5 days</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">Billable Person-Days</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-4 text-center">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto mb-2 text-[#FF6B6B]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
        </svg>
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1B2A4A]">$1,400/day</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">Blended Daily Rate</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Delivery -->
    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1B2A4A] mt-6 mb-3">Delivery</h4>

