        <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">Multi-Tenant Fixed Cost</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      <strong>The delivery model is a full solution handover.</strong> At the end of the engagement,
      Cloud9 owns the application, the source code, the infrastructure, and the operational knowledge
      to run and maintain it independently. There is no ongoing maintenance contract. See <button type="button" onclick="showSection('the-cost')" class="text-[#FF6B6B] hover:underline cursor-pointer font-medium">Section 7</button>
      and <button type="button" onclick="showSection('support-model')" class="text-[#FF6B6B] hover:underline cursor-pointer font-medium">Section 17</button> for full details.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 2: Who We Are -->
<section data-section="who-we-are" class="proposal-section hidden">
  <div class="proposal-content">
    <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1B2A4A] mb-6">2. Who We Are</h2>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      BrightKeep is a Digital Product &amp; Business Development company. We both build technology
      solutions, and consult on how to build them. We are founded on decades of experience delivering
      in the digital sector across corporate, startup, and consulting environments.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      We are a product-focussed firm, starting with the problem to solve, not the technology. Our
      engagement process starts with what the customer or business needs, and we shape solutions around
      outcomes rather than tool preferences. We favour pragmatic development &mdash; solutions that are
      understandable, maintainable, and right-sized for where the product&rsquo;s maturity is, with
      clear paths to scale when ready.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1B2A4A] mt-8 mb-4">Relevant Experience</h3>

    <div class="space-y-4 mt-6 mb-6">
      <!-- NightOffice.ai -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5">
        <img
          src="/proposals/nightoffice.png"
          alt="NightOffice.ai"
          class="w-full sm:w-48 h-36 object-cover rounded-lg flex-shrink-0"
        />
        <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#1B2A4A] mb-2">NightOffice.ai</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed mb-3 flex-1">
            SaaS platform giving entrepreneurs access to AI-powered specialists across Finance,
            Engineering, and Marketing. Built on React, Supabase, real-time collaboration, and
            multi-agent coordination.
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-[#FF6B6B]/10 text-[#FF6B6B] self-start">AI agents, real-time data, multi-user SaaS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Solution Documentation Platform -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5">
        <img
          src="/proposals/solution-documentation.png"
          alt="Solution Documentation Platform"
          class="w-full sm:w-48 h-36 object-cover rounded-lg flex-shrink-0"
        />
        <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#1B2A4A] mb-2">Solution Documentation Platform</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed mb-3 flex-1">
            Tool integrating GitHub repositories and CI/CD pipelines into Microsoft Power Platform,
            using AI to analyse codebases and generate technical documentation.
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-[#FF6B6B]/10 text-[#FF6B6B] self-start">Microsoft ecosystem, AI integration, data pipelines</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Financial Analytics Dashboard -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5">
        <img
          src="/proposals/financial-analytics.png"
          alt="Financial Analytics Dashboard"
          class="w-full sm:w-48 h-36 object-cover rounded-lg flex-shrink-0"
        />
        <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#1B2A4A] mb-2">Financial Analytics Dashboard</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed mb-3 flex-1">
            Solution pulling data from multiple sources into interactive dashboards for financial
            forecasting, pricing model evaluation, and performance tracking.
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-[#FF6B6B]/10 text-[#FF6B6B] self-start">Data visualisation, multi-source integration</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#6B7280] text-sm">
      Full company and team details are in <button type="button" onclick="showSection('solution-detailed')" class="text-[#FF6B6B] hover:underline cursor-pointer font-medium">Section 8.6</button>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 3: The Problem -->
<section data-section="the-problem" class="proposal-section hidden">
  <div class="proposal-content">
    <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1B2A4A] mb-6">3. The Problem</h2>

    <p class="mb-6 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      Cloud9&rsquo;s consultants map application integrations and dependencies as part of their client
      engagements. Today, this is done using SharePoint lists, manually drawn diagrams, and institutional
      knowledge.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#FF6B6B] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126ZM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008Z" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#1B2A4A] mb-1">Diagrams go stale immediately</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">The moment a diagram is drawn, the landscape changes. There is no connection between the diagram and the source data.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#FF6B6B] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126ZM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008Z" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#1B2A4A] mb-1">Redrawing for different audiences wastes time</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">An executive wants a simplified view. An architect wants protocols. A developer wants API details. Each audience requires a separate diagram, drawn from scratch.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#FF6B6B] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126ZM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008Z" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#1B2A4A] mb-1">No single source of truth</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">Integration knowledge lives in the heads of individual consultants, in scattered SharePoint lists, and in static images that may or may not reflect reality.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#FF6B6B] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126ZM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008Z" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#1B2A4A] mb-1">Impact analysis is manual</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">Tracing the consequences of decommissioning an application requires a consultant to follow connections by hand across spreadsheets.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      The visualisation tool replaces manual diagramming with a living, interactive integration map
      that pulls directly from structured data, renders dynamically for different audiences, and
      persists across the lifecycle of a client engagement.
    </p>
